subject: College Athletics
Basketball
lead_paragraph: Jeff Adrien scored 18 points and Hasheem Thabeet added 14 points, 11 rebounds and 4 blocks for the Huskies (21-1, 10-1 Big East), who rolled to their 10th straight victory.
